synopsis.value: We travel through the strange landscape of the Astral Plane and eventually come across a small Gith military outpost. Here we find Kith'rak Voss. Hes exhausted and weak, but a malevolent triumph still sparkles in his eyes: were too late. He already sent the outposts scouts ahead. Its only a matter of time before word reaches Vlaakith. Now he will fulfill his duty and kill us.
